Lighting switch - control box to headlamp relays
High Beam - headlamp dip switch to high beam relay
Low Beam - headlamp dip switch to low beam relay
Headlamp dip switch to high beam indicator light
Headlamp switch to headlamp dip switch (high/low)
Headlamp flasher unit to headlamp flasher microswitch
Low beam - headlamp relay to light
High beam - headlamp relay to light
Headlamp switch to headlamp flasher relay
Hot all time, unfused. Main battery lead, control box to solenoid & rear courtesy lights
ignition switch (pos.1) to window switches and hazard flash unit.
Control box (compensated voltage control only) to ignition switch and lighting switch (feed)
Dynamo to control box to 'no charge' warning light.
Hot with ignition on, fused. Accessories fused via ignition switch;
Fuse box to reverse switch, wiper motor, heated rear screen switch, heater fan switch, heater switch to heater fan, washer switch (connects
to white/lightgreen), independent flasher unit brake failure warning light, handbrake switch, brake lights switch, voltage stabilizer, voltage
stabilizer to fuel gauge, hazard switch to turn signal switch, ignition switch (pos. 4) to radio.
Fuel gauge to fuel tank sender unit or changeover switch or voltage stabilizer to tank sender.
Stop lamp switch to stop lamps, or stop lamp switch to lamp failure unit, indicator flasher unit to indicator warning light.
Indicator stalk to left hand indicators
Indicator stalk to right hand indicators
Heater motor to switch single speed (or to 'slow' on two or three speed motor)
Hazard flasher switch to hazard flasher unit
Windscreen washer switch to washer pump
Indicator flasher unit to indicator stalk
Handbrake switch to handbrake warning light
Hazard flasher switch to warning light
Hot all the time, fused. Accessories fed directly from battery via fuse (incl. horn & cigar lighter)
Horn to horn push, anti-theft switch to horn
Interior lights to switch (subsidiary circuit door safety lights to switch)
Main feed to all running lights mastered by sidelamp switch. Sidelights and number plate lights.
Brake servo warning light indicator, servo to warning light, brake failure warning light test switch to light.
Dash lights, panel switch to cigar lighter, window switch power lead to dash courtesy light.
Hot with ignition on, unfused. Ignition switch (pos. 2) to coil, ignition warning light, fuse box (for green)
anti-theft switch between ignition switch and fuse box.
Headlamp flasher relay to high beam lights circuit
Ignition switch (pos. 4) to fuse box (for purple)
Ignition coil contact breaker to distributor contact breaker
Headlamp flasher relay to headlamp flasher unit
